snippet.title: Air Raid 3 (PS2 Gameplay)
snippet.description: Air Raid 3 offers you the unique chance to become a heroic jet fighter pilot, with numerous missions all over the world, that will stun even the most experienced gamers. Guide your plane through the enemies areas and destroy their planes inorder to eliminate the opposition's airforce units, by using a selection of advanced guns and extreme missiles, use your anti-lock radars to avoid enemy gun and missile fire at all costs as you will not be the only one that has an extremely advanced setup fighter plane and weapons, the future of the world as we know it lies in your hands... 15 Levels and continous changing of the opposition's strategy, weapons and appearance, ensure many hours of action packed fun.
